---
import { Picture } from "astro:assets";
import heroImage from "assets/dragonos.png";
import Link from "@components/ui/link.astro";
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
---

<main
  class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 place-items-center pt-16 pb-8 md:pt-12 md:pb-24">
  <div class="py-6 md:order-1">
    <Picture
      src={heroImage}
      alt="DragonOS"
      loading="eager"
    />
  </div>
  <div>
    <h1
      class="text-5xl lg:text-6xl xl:text-7xl font-bold lg:tracking-tight xl:tracking-tighter">
      开源，共创未来！
    </h1>
    <p class="text-lg mt-4 text-slate-600 max-w-xl">
      DragonOS 是使用 Rust 从 〇 自研内核，具有 Linux兼容性 的操作系统，面向云计算 
      Serverless 场景而设计。<wbr /> 
    </p>
    <p class="text-lg mt-4 text-slate-600 max-w-xl">
      DragonOS is an operating system developed 
      from scratch using Rust, with Linux compatibility. It is designed for 
      Serverless scenarios.
    </p>
    <div class="mt-6 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3">
      <Link
        href="#"
        href="https://github.com/DragonOS-Community/DragonOS"
        target="_blank"
        class="flex gap-1 items-center justify-center"
        rel="noopener">
        <Icon class="text-white w-5 h-5" name="bx:bxl-github" />

         项目仓库
      </Link>
      <Link
        size="lg"
        style="outline"
        rel="noopener"
        href="https://bbs.dragonos.org.cn/"
        class="flex gap-1 items-center justify-center"
        target="_blank">
        <Icon class="text-black w-4 h-4" name="bx:bxl-discourse" />
         加入社区
      </Link>
    </div>
  </div>
</main>
